data.description: Welcome to paradise in Hernando Beach, Discover the essence of coastal living in this meticulously kept and updated 3-bedroom, 2-bath spread over two spacious stories situated on a double lot. Dive into the saltwater pool, surrounded by tranquility and modern elegance. Feel secure with the certification of elevation, offering some peace of mind in this slice of paradise as well as a fully fenced back and side yard.Boating enthusiasts will delight in the mere 30-second drive to the nearby boat marina ramp, while breathtaking water views enhance the allure of this coastal retreat. Enjoy the convenience of close proximity to shopping centers, adding practicality to the picturesque setting. This home isn't just a sanctuary; it's a gateway to a vibrant layer-back lifestyle. Immerse yourself in the local scene with waterfront restaurants, bars, and shops. Your coastal dream home, blending comfort and sophistication, awaits in this coveted Hernando Beach/Weeki Wachee community. This home also doubles as a great income producing property for short term rentals year round for those who travel frequently. This is a very affordable home for this neighborhood and is priced to sell. Don't miss out, come take a look before it's gone!
